Add pre-generated encoding/type headers extracted from the upstream release
tarball (freetds-1.4.22.tar.gz from freetds.org).  These files are produced
by Perl scripts + gperf during a repository build, but are distributed
pre-built in release tarballs.  When HAVE_PERL_SOURCES=false (i.e. gperf is
not available) the Makefile expects them to already be present.

